<h2>Architecture</h2>
<p>The MVC pattern separates your application into three main layers:</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>Model</strong>: Manages data and business logic.</li>
    <li><strong>View</strong>: Handles presentation and HTML rendering.</li>
    <li><strong>Controller</strong>: Orchestrates the flow between models and views.</li>
</ul>

